---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="site-shell">
		<header class="nav" aria-label="Primary">
			<a class="wordmark" href="/" aria-label="Zake home">
				<span class="mark">Z</span>
				<span>Zake</span>
			</a>
			<nav>
				<a href="#why">Why</a>
				<a href="#media">Media</a>
				<a href="#install">Install</a>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
			<div class="hero-copy">
				<p class="kicker">Alpha terminal notebook manager</p>
				<h1 id="hero-title">Markdown notes stay yours. Git keeps memory honest.</h1>
				<p class="lede">
					Zake is a fast terminal UI for organizing plain Markdown notebooks,
					metadata, links, search results, and Git changes without turning into
					another closed note app.
				</p>
				<div class="hero-actions" aria-label="Quick links">
					<a class="button primary" href="#install">Install from source</a>
					<a class="button secondary" href="#why">Why it exists</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<aside class="terminal" aria-label="Zake quickstart terminal">
				<div class="terminal-bar">
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
				</div>
				<pre><code>$ cargo install --path .
$ zake init ~/notes
$ cd ~/notes
$ zake

notes        git status        backlinks
ideas.md     modified          clean
today.md     staged            4 links</code></pre>
			</aside>
		</section>

		<section id="why" class="section why" aria-labelledby="why-title">
			<div>
				<p class="kicker">Why it exists</p>
				<h2 id="why-title">Most note apps want to own the room.</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="stack">
				<p>
					Zake exists for people who already trust Markdown, Git, ripgrep, and
					their editor. It gives those tools one focused control surface, then
					gets out of the way.
				</p>
				<p>
					It does not hide note files, replace your editor, or invent a private
					sync format. Your notebook remains a folder of readable files with
					YAML frontmatter and normal Git history.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="proof-grid" aria-label="Core principles">
			<article>
				<span class="number">01</span>
				<h3>Portable by default</h3>
				<p>Plain Markdown notes, YAML frontmatter, and Git history live in your notebook folder.</p>
			</article>
			<article>
				<span class="number">02</span>
				<h3>Terminal-first</h3>
				<p>Move through notes, tags, backlinks, search, and Git state without leaving the keyboard.</p>
			</article>
			<article>
				<span class="number">03</span>
				<h3>Editor-respecting</h3>
				<p>Zake opens note bodies in <code>$EDITOR</code>. It manages context, not prose.</p>
			</article>
		</section>

		<section class="section alpha" aria-labelledby="alpha-title">
			<div>
				<p class="kicker">Alpha state</p>
				<h2 id="alpha-title">Useful foundation, sharp edges possible.</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="warning">
				<p>
					Zake is early software. Use it at your own risk, keep backups, and
					review Git changes before committing important notebooks.
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Working TUI, CLI helpers, Git wrappers, and ripgrep-backed search.</li>
					<li>No in-app body editor and no full note reading view by design.</li>
					<li>Release binaries are planned; source install is current path.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="media" class="media-section" aria-labelledby="media-title">
			<div class="section-heading">
				<p class="kicker">Videos and screenshots</p>
				<h2 id="media-title">A quiet place for demos when they land.</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="media-grid">
				<article class="media-card feature">
					<div class="placeholder video">
						<span class="play" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						<p>TUI walkthrough video</p>
					</div>
					<h3>Notebook control surface</h3>
					<p>Show pane navigation, fuzzy search, metadata, and Git staging.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="media-card">
					<div class="placeholder lines">
						<span></span>
						<span></span>
						<span></span>
					</div>
					<h3>Search and graph health</h3>
					<p>Feature screenshots for backlinks, broken links, or orphan notes.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="media-card">
					<div class="placeholder split">
						<span></span>
						<span></span>
					</div>
					<h3>Git history flow</h3>
					<p>Drop in images for status, diff, snapshot, and history views.</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="install" class="install" aria-labelledby="install-title">
			<div>
				<p class="kicker">Install</p>
				<h2 id="install-title">Build once, then run <code>zake</code>.</h2>
				<p>
					Requires Git and ripgrep for full workflow. Rust is needed only when
					installing from source.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="install-panel">
				<ol>
					<li>
						<span>Clone repository</span>
						<code>git clone https://github.com/devaldrete/zake.git</code>
					</li>
					<li>
						<span>Install binary</span>
						<code>cd zake && cargo install --path .</code>
					</li>
					<li>
						<span>Create notebook</span>
						<code>zake init ~/notes && cd ~/notes</code>
					</li>
					<li>
						<span>Start TUI</span>
						<code>zake</code>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	:global(body) {
		background: #f4f1e8;
		color: #1b1c18;
		font-family: "Iowan Old Style", "Palatino Linotype", Palatino, serif;
	}

	:global(a) {
		color: inherit;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.site-shell {
		width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 24px 0 56px;
	}

	.nav {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 24px;
		padding: 10px 0 42px;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.wordmark,
	.nav nav,
	.hero-actions {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.wordmark {
		gap: 10px;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
	}

	.mark {
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		width: 34px;
		height: 34px;
		border: 1px solid #1b1c18;
		background: #d7ff51;
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
	}

	.nav nav {
		gap: 8px;
	}

	.nav nav a {
		padding: 8px 10px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
	}

	.nav nav a:hover {
		border-color: #1b1c18;
	}

	.hero {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(320px, 0.8fr);
		gap: 56px;
		align-items: end;
		min-height: 68vh;
		padding-bottom: 72px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.2);
	}

	.kicker {
		margin: 0 0 14px;
		color: #6b3f1d;
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	h1,
	h2,
	h3,
	p {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	h1 {
		max-width: 870px;
		margin-bottom: 26px;
		font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 6vw, 5.8rem);
		line-height: 0.94;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0;
	}

	h2 {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 4.6rem);
		line-height: 0.95;
		letter-spacing: 0;
	}

	h3 {
		margin-bottom: 12px;
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	.lede {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin-bottom: 28px;
		color: #34362f;
		font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.45rem);
		line-height: 1.45;
	}

	.hero-actions {
		gap: 12px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.button {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 46px;
		padding: 12px 18px;
		border: 1px solid #1b1c18;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.button.primary {
		background: #1b1c18;
		color: #f4f1e8;
	}

	.button.secondary {
		background: #d7ff51;
	}

	.terminal {
		border: 1px solid #1b1c18;
		background: #11120f;
		box-shadow: 14px 14px 0 #d7ff51;
		color: #e7eadc;
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
	}

	.terminal-bar {
		display: flex;
		gap: 7px;
		padding: 14px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 241, 232, 0.18);
	}

	.terminal-bar span {
		width: 10px;
		height: 10px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: #d7ff51;
	}

	.terminal pre {
		overflow-x: auto;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 22px;
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	.section,
	.install {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
		gap: 56px;
		padding: 86px 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.2);
	}

	.stack p,
	.warning p,
	.install p,
	.media-card p,
	.proof-grid p {
		color: #3b3d35;
		font-size: 1.06rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.proof-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.2);
	}

	.proof-grid article {
		min-height: 280px;
		padding: 28px;
		border-right: 1px solid rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.2);
	}

	.proof-grid article:last-child {
		border-right: 0;
	}

	.number {
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 76px;
		color: #6b3f1d;
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.warning {
		border-left: 5px solid #c24825;
		padding-left: 24px;
	}

	.warning ul {
		margin: 22px 0 0;
		padding-left: 20px;
		color: #3b3d35;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.media-section {
		padding: 86px 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.2);
	}

	.section-heading {
		max-width: 690px;
		margin-bottom: 34px;
	}

	.media-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.9fr 0.9fr;
		gap: 18px;
	}

	.media-card {
		border: 1px solid #1b1c18;
		background: #eee9dc;
		padding: 16px;
	}

	.placeholder {
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		min-height: 220px;
		margin-bottom: 18px;
		border: 1px dashed rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.55);
		background:
			linear-gradient(rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px),
			linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
		background-size: 22px 22px;
	}

	.media-card.feature .placeholder {
		min-height: 318px;
	}

	.video {
		gap: 14px;
		align-content: center;
	}

	.play {
		width: 58px;
		height: 58px;
		border: 1px solid #1b1c18;
		background: #d7ff51;
		clip-path: polygon(22% 12%, 22% 88%, 88% 50%);
	}

	.placeholder p {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.lines,
	.split {
		place-items: stretch;
		padding: 26px;
		gap: 16px;
	}

	.lines span,
	.split span {
		display: block;
		border: 1px solid rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.55);
		background: rgba(215, 255, 81, 0.42);
	}

	.lines span:nth-child(1) {
		height: 40px;
	}

	.lines span:nth-child(2) {
		height: 92px;
	}

	.lines span:nth-child(3) {
		height: 56px;
	}

	.split {
		grid-template-columns: 0.75fr 1.25fr;
	}

	.install {
		align-items: start;
		padding-bottom: 0;
		border-bottom: 0;
	}

	.install-panel {
		border: 1px solid #1b1c18;
		background: #1b1c18;
		color: #f4f1e8;
	}

	.install-panel ol {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		list-style: none;
		counter-reset: install;
	}

	.install-panel li {
		display: grid;
		gap: 10px;
		padding: 22px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 241, 232, 0.18);
		counter-increment: install;
	}

	.install-panel li:last-child {
		border-bottom: 0;
	}

	.install-panel span {
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.install-panel span::before {
		content: counter(install, decimal-leading-zero) " / ";
		color: #d7ff51;
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
	}

	code {
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
	}

	.install-panel code {
		overflow-x: auto;
		padding: 11px 12px;
		background: rgba(244, 241, 232, 0.08);
		color: #e7eadc;
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	@media (max-width: 860px) {
		.site-shell {
			width: min(100% - 28px, 680px);
			padding-top: 16px;
		}

		.nav {
			align-items: flex-start;
			padding-bottom: 32px;
		}

		.hero,
		.section,
		.install,
		.media-grid,
		.proof-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.hero {
			min-height: auto;
			gap: 34px;
			padding-bottom: 56px;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: clamp(3.15rem, 14vw, 4.9rem);
		}

		.terminal {
			box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 #d7ff51;
		}

		.section,
		.media-section,
		.install {
			gap: 28px;
			padding: 58px 0;
		}

		.proof-grid article {
			min-height: 0;
			border-right: 0;
			border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27, 28, 24, 0.2);
		}

		.proof-grid article:last-child {
			border-bottom: 0;
		}

		.number {
			margin-bottom: 36px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 540px) {
		.nav {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.nav nav {
			width: 100%;
			justify-content: space-between;
		}

		.hero-actions {
			align-items: stretch;
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.button {
			width: 100%;
		}

		.terminal pre,
		.install-panel code {
			font-size: 0.78rem;
		}

		.media-card.feature .placeholder,
		.placeholder {
			min-height: 210px;
		}
	}
</style>
